1. for sending preserved signals, use signal()
2. for sending customed signals, use sigaction()
3. customed signals should be presented as 'SIGUSER1 + n' or 'SIGUSER2 + n'
4. there will be an error 141 exit if the customed signal which was sent to server was not handled by sigaction() in server code

man pages:
man signal, man 2 kill, man 7 signal
